replies.body:
I've been loving how many events League has been having for awhile now to be honest. The introduction to Missions and how they've continued to evolve as well has been really interesting; the pathways easily let for all players to do them while giving an option for a more difficult path if you choose. The rewards are definitely enjoyable at the end of the day. (Although the Hextech Crafting system overall still could use some changes imo.)

I'm looking forward to this event and the fun things that should come with it. Patch 8.11 is gonna be an interesting one with the changes to both SR and ARAM. Looking forward to seeing the Bilgewater ARAM map again too.
{{sticker:sg-kiko}}
